description.p:
According to an aspect of the invention, a receiver comprises:
a bandpass filter module operable to filter an inbound wireless signal to produce a filtered inbound wireless signal having a bandwidth;
a sample and hold module operable to sample and hold, at a rate corresponding to a multiple of the bandwidth of the filtered inbound wireless signal, the filtered inbound wireless signal to produce a frequency domain sample pulse train;
a discrete time filter module operable to filter the frequency domain sample pulse train to produce a filtered sample pulse; and
a conversion module operable to convert the filtered sample pulse into an inbound baseband signal.

Advantageously, the receiver further comprises:
a clock generation circuit including:
a clock generation module operable to generate a system clock signal;
a sample and hold clock module operable to generate, from the system clock signal, a sample and hold clock signal at the rate corresponding to the multiple of the bandwidth of the filtered inbound wireless signal;
a discrete time filter clock module operable to generate a filter clock from the system clock signal; and
a conversion clock module operable to generate a conversion clock signal from the system clock signal.

According to an aspect, a receiver comprises:
a bandpass filter module operable to filter an inbound wireless signal to produce a filtered inbound wireless signal having a bandwidth;
a sample and hold module operable to sample and hold, at a rate corresponding to a multiple of the bandwidth of the filtered inbound wireless signal, the filtered inbound wireless signal to produce a frequency domain sample pulse train;
a discrete time filter module having a baseband bandpass filter response operable to filter the frequency domain sample pulse train to produce a filtered baseband sample pulse; and
an analog to digital conversion module operable to convert the filtered baseband sample pulse into an inbound baseband signal.

Advantageously, the receiver further comprises:
a clock generation circuit including:
a clock generation module operable to generate a system clock signal;
a sample and hold clock module operable to generate, from the system clock signal, a sample and hold clock signal at the rate corresponding to the multiple of the bandwidth of the filtered inbound wireless signal;
a discrete time filter clock module operable to generate a filter clock from the system clock signal; and
a conversion clock module operable to generate a conversion clock signal from the system clock signal.

According to an aspect, a transceiver comprises:
a receiver section including:
a bandpass filter module operable to filter an inbound wireless signal to produce a filtered inbound wireless signal having a bandwidth;
a receive sample and hold module operable to sample and hold, at a rate corresponding to a multiple of the bandwidth of the filtered inbound wireless signal, the filtered inbound wireless signal to produce a receive frequency domain sample pulse train;
a receive discrete time filter module operable to filter the receive frequency domain sample pulse train to produce a filtered sample pulse; and
a receive conversion module operable to convert the filtered sample pulse into an inbound baseband signal; and
a transmitter section including:
a transmit conversion module operable to convert an outbound baseband signal into an outbound frequency domain pulse that has a bandwidth;
a transmit sample and hold module operable to sample and hold, at a rate corresponding to a multiple of the bandwidth of the outbound frequency domain pulse, the outbound frequency domain pulse to produce a transmit frequency domain sample pulse train; and a transmit discrete time filter module having a wireless frequency bandpass filter response operable to filter the transmit frequency domain sample pulse train to produce an outbound wireless signal.

Advantageously, the transceiver further comprises:
a clock generation circuit including:
a clock generation module operable to generate a system clock signal;
a sample and hold clock module operable to generate, from the system clock signal, a receive sample and hold clock signal and a transmit sample and hold clock signal;
a discrete time filter clock module operable to generate, from the system clock signal, a receive filter clock and a transmit filter clock; and
a conversion clock module operable to generate, from the system clock signal, a receive conversion clock signal and a transmit conversion clock signal.

claim.claim-text:
A receiver comprises:
a bandpass filter module operable to filter an inbound wireless signal to produce a filtered inbound wireless signal having a bandwidth;
a sample and hold module operable to sample and hold, at a rate corresponding to a multiple of the bandwidth of the filtered inbound wireless signal, the filtered inbound wireless signal to produce a frequency domain sample pulse train;
a discrete time filter module having a baseband bandpass filter response operable to filter the frequency domain sample pulse train to produce a filtered baseband sample pulse; and
an analog to digital conversion module operable to convert the filtered baseband sample pulse into an inbound baseband signal.
